item.title: I think its fixed
item.description: I needed a quick break while working on yellowikis.us. a site that is supposed to take over the world (we shall see… we shall see…) - so i fixored my blog. pictures and tags should work again and it should now rock. i need to tweak the theme a bit. make it less busy and then make it so the technology section is acceptable by 3gcoding.com. i really like jakes site.
